## Decisions and Action Items

* **Hybrid PAKE Draft Split:** Christopher Wood will restructure the hybrid PAKE draft to separate the core cryptographic primitives (for CFRG) from the protocol-specific wire formats (for a future IETF working group / BoF) before initiating an adoption call.
* **Longfellow Draft Split:** The authors of the Longfellow ZK draft will coordinate with the authors of the Fiat-Shamir draft to integrate the IOP sections and refine the core scheme/parameters document.

